{"tid":640880,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】鹽與聖所，之後可能玩殘廢被PUBG Day200 24/4","createTime":"2018-04-24T15:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T17:46:43.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1923cfc859c2c217cfdb8eced8343778ff28dcac","tid":640880,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T15:07:11.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=as9LQJ0q1zqmooOgAV5qMNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=8acc5af7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=as9LQJ0q1zqmooOgAV5qMNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=31573000\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"328410b1ede30d34fd51c6d55c111002bf5310c8","tid":640880,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T15:10:07.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa11c365a92dba3206846dcbe3aadb0bcbb05fbb","tid":640880,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T15:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d8206e793047a7a9655a1caeea5552c61d55b8c","tid":640880